Rule 15    program -> statement
Rule 16    statement -> LSQRBRACKET LSQRBRACKET statement RSQRBRACKET NEWLINE statement RSQRBRACKET
Rule 17    statement -> PRINTLN LSQRBRACKET arglist RSQRBRACKET
Rule 18    arglist -> arglist COMMA expression
Rule 19    arglist -> expression

Terminals, with rules where they appear

COMMA                : 18
DIVIDE               : 6
EQUALS               : 10
IDENTIFIER           : 9 10
LPARENTH             : 1
LSQRBRACKET          : 16 16 17
MINUS                : 3 4
NEWLINE              : 12 14 16
NUMBER               : 7
PLUS                 : 2
PRINTLN              : 17
RPARENTH             : 1
RSQRBRACKET          : 16 16 17
STRING               : 8
TIMES                : 5
